Class BigraphIsoPredicate<B extends Bigraph<? extends Signature<?>>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.tudresden.inf.st.bigraphs.core.reactivesystem.ReactiveSystemPredicates<B>

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Predicate<B>
    public class BigraphIsoPredicate<B extends Bigraph<? extends Signature<?>>>
extends ReactiveSystemPredicates<B>
    Predicate implementation that returns true if two bigraphs are isomorphic (i.e., structurally equivalent).

    A predicate can be created by using the static methods the class provides.

    Bigraph isomorphism is checked using the canonical string encoding.

    Author:
    Dominik Grzelak
